HEADWORD: Aurochloride
<hw>Au`ro*chlo"ride</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Aurum</ets> + <ets>chloride</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>The trichloride of gold combination with the chloride of another
